idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;"> uh, this</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0=
;">The access to capital comes at a time of reckoning for the truckmaker, w=
