om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Legal realism</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I feel like most regulation of big bus=
iness <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24569402.275=
148/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9hb24td2lsbGlzLXRvd2Vycy13YXRzb24=
